'''''ST 178''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class shuttle]] in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]]. The "ST" in the shuttle's designation stood for "space transport".<ref name="PM">{{SWPM|set=Base Set|cardname=''ST 178 Lambda''-class shuttle|link=http://www.swpocketmodels.com/images/ship19.jpg}}</ref>

A black [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] logo and the [[Starship/Legends|ship's]] numeric designation were painted on the tips of the port and starboard wings. Although most Imperial shuttles boasted better defensive systems, ''ST 178'' was armed with both [[Proton torpedo/Legends|proton torpedoes]] and [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolasers]] (weapons usually installed on [[IPV-1 System Patrol Craft|Imperial patrol vehicles]]) in addition to the laser cannon emplacements standard for its class.<ref name="PM" />

